How to create a package:

ulyaoth-tomcat-native:
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-tomcat-native/build-tomcat-native.sh ; chmod +x build-tomcat-native.sh ; ./build-tomcat-native.sh

ulyaoth-tomcat-native1.2:
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ulyaoth/repository/master/ulyaoth-tomcat-native/build-tomcat-native1.2.sh ; chmod +x build-tomcat-native1.2.sh ; ./build-tomcat-native1.2.sh